Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Equal rights crusade goes on
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043x8v1
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 7 Aug 1983
Senator Sam Ervin becomes new opponent in ongoing fight for Equal Rights Amendment. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less